    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that \"beauty\" feels so forced. like trying to put a bandaid on a void. if the outcome is always zero, then the struggle to find meaning is just a way of lying to ourselves to keep the lights on. it feels more honest to just accept that the struggle is pointless and stop fighting it.",
